# ============================================================
# WHITELIST GITIGNORE — SENSITIVE DATA PROTECTION
# ============================================================
# This repo will contain/reference an Obsidian vault with highly
# sensitive personal data (journal entries, chat history, recovery
# content). Safety-first: everything is ignored by default.
# Only explicitly approved paths are tracked.
# ============================================================

# Ignore everything at the top level by default
/*

# --- Explicitly tracked root files ---
!.gitignore
!CLAUDE.md
!README.md

# --- Explicitly tracked directories ---
!.claude/
!.github/
!creek-tools/
!plans/
**/git-issues/
!scripts/

# --- Obsidian vault folder structure ---
# Allow top-level vault folders (scaffold only — .gitkeep files)
!00-Creek-Meta/
!01-Fragments/
!02-Threads/
!03-Eddies/
!04-Praxis/
!05-Wavelength/
!06-Frequencies/
!07-Voice/
!08-Decisions/
!09-Reference/
!10-Liminal/

# --- Obsidian configuration ---
!.obsidian/
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/cache

# ============================================================
# OBSIDIAN VAULT — SENSITIVE CONTENT (NEVER TRACK)
# ============================================================
# Vault directories are whitelisted above so the folder scaffold
# (.gitkeep files) is tracked.  Everything EXCEPT .gitkeep inside
# those directories is ignored below to protect sensitive content.
# Only 00-Creek-Meta/Scripts/ content should ever be tracked.
# ============================================================

# Vault content directories — ignore everything except .gitkeep
